    All the possible license statuses of the library. The SdkStatus helps to check if license file is valid and correct. Those statuses inform current library state. The LICENSE_VERIFICATION_OK means that license file is found and it is correct for current package. The LICENSE_VERIFICATION_EVALUATION status shows that license file is absent and library is functioning in the trial mode. The LICENSE_VERIFICATION_LIMIT_REACHED status shows that license file is absent and amount of scans reached the maximum value and library will scan no more codes. All other license statuses show that some errors occurred during license checking process.
